    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Medium model risk. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 compression-bending is the regulatory standard for this device class and no additional loading modes are claimed in the COU. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
